snippet.title: Heroes of Hammerwatch, Witch Hunter, Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Witch Hunter is the dlc that brings you all new content to Heroes of Hammerwatch, with a new class and a lot of added gameplay-features.

http://www.heroesofhammerwatch.com

Game is available on Steam and Gog.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086870/Heroes_of_Hammerwatch_Witch_Hunter/

https://www.gog.com/game/heroes_of_hammerwatch

Crackshell Twitter for faster updates: https://twitter.com/RealCrackshell
